ges are done, you must build the docker image and verify that it works locally by making api calls if applicable.\\n- Then only you can mark it as completed and submit the implementation.\\n- Every component must have `workload.yaml` at its root, refer to the github task.\\n\\nDo **not** run `git` yourself. Do **not** create PRs or branches. Submission triggers commit → push → OpenChoreo build → deploy automatically.\\n\"}]},\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"session_id\":\"c8782c7c-553e-46ce-bc01-b2dc289a5619\",\"uuid\":\"9bcaa59f-ec6f-42bc-b880-677d15d0af58\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\"{\"type\"{\"{\"typ{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01ERpDiXU2x6FApbZXnJUx6B\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"The user wants me to work on a GitHub issue at https://github.com/asdlc-repos/mxcz308/issues/10. Let me start by using the ASDLC MCP tools to get the project context and then look at the GitHub issue.\\n\\nLet me first fetch the GitHub issue using the gh CLI, and also use the ASDLC MCP tools to get context.\",\"signature\":\"\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"stop_details\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":416,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":11113,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":416,\"{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_012ESiz2PYxH9atRf5RmAKK8\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01MPrVmZNDq{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01ERpDiXU2x6FApbZXnJUx6B\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01MJMCTzUbsRQ2598z8dnY24\",\"name\":\"ToolSearch\",\"input\":{\"query\":\"select:mcp__asdlc__get_proje